('gasir_fermented_sheeps_head_smalahove_style_faroese', 'Gásir (Fermented Sheep''s Head / Smalahove Style)', 178, 20.5, 0.0, 11.0, 0.0, 0.0, 150, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['gásir (fermented sheep''s head / smalahove style)', 'sheep''s head', 'smalahove', 'salted sheep head'], 'traditional', NULL, 1, 'FO', 'Salted and wind-dried sheep''s head prepared in the Faroese tradition; a rare delicacy similar to Norwegian smalahove. Historically consumed at winter festivals when slaughter season ended.', TRUE),
